{"tid":1141594,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"導演陳小娟係公屋出身，中大神科畢業，初執導即拍下神作《淪落人》","createTime":"2019-05-06T14:41:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-07T10:47:46.000Z","uid":57036,"like":108,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"24c36c79c03472fb9fd890d43abd4fb31c4dc825","tid":1141594,"uid":57036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T14:41:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/電影/318072/淪落人-專訪-為夢想放棄高薪厚職-新晉導演陳小娟崛起之路\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1%2F318072%2F%E6%B7%AA%E8%90%BD%E4%BA%BA-%E5%B0%88%E8%A8%AA-%E7%82%BA%E5%A4%A2%E6%83%B3%E6%94%BE%E6%A3%84%E9%AB%98%E8%96%AA%E5%8E%9A%E8%81%B7-%E6%96%B0%E6%99%89%E5%B0%8E%E6%BC%94%E9%99%B3%E5%B0%8F%E5%A8%9F%E5%B4%9B%E8%B5%B7%E4%B9%8B%E8%B7%AF&d=9OMcXw0STyGFZrzowU4xHpNY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=e687e925\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/電影/318072/淪落人-專訪-為夢想放棄高薪厚職-新晉導演陳小娟崛起之路</a><br />\n<br />\n睇完淪落人，真係無諗過咁高汁<br />\n題材大膽，夠膽用香港人鄙視既賓賓做女主角<br />\n拍攝簡單，低成本製作，但情節舖排屌打xx風雲yy風暴<br />\n角色唔多，但每個人物都發揮得淋漓盡致<br />\n<br />\n究竟邊個執導咁厲害<br />\n原來係個新晉導演，叫陳小娟，公屋出身，神科畢業<br />\n佢冇隨波逐流，加入高薪厚職既銀行/投資界<br />\n反而勇於追求自己既夢想，擺脫旁人既冷眼<br />\n毅然投身電影界，為港產片留下一大傑作<br />\n希望大家多d認識佢同支持佢<br />\n繼續拍更加有意義有質素既電影"},{"pid":"19e0a339d438045e9c274274ddbcf3442c1b29c5","tid":1141594,"uid":57036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T15:01:32.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bf1812be40e81ddff3acefab6660b2852bb9d3d","tid":1141594,"uid":57036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T15:17:35.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de0ddef914d47a6cf9bb0915fcef4e775